description.en: Morning exercise is just like a button; when you press it, it's time for your body to greet today lively. When exercising is being a part of daily morning habits, just like a chain reaction, you will have a more stable circadian rhythm. A sleepy daytime or a sleepless nighttime won't bother you anymore.
description.zh-Hans: 晨间运动，就像一个开关，当你按动了它，身体便会知道是时候带着活力去迎接新的一天。当运动成为晨间习惯时，如连锁反应一般，一日的作息会更加规律，醒后疲乏或是入睡困难，将不再困扰你。
description.zh-Hant: 晨間運動，就像一個開關，當你按動了它，身體便會知道是時候帶著活力去迎接新的一天。當運動成為晨間習慣時，如連鎖反應一般，一日的作息會更加規律，醒後疲乏或是入睡困難，將不再困擾你。

description.en: Each day is a journey passing through time, while a lunch-break, like a gas station, allows you to refuel energy for your body.
